Theming utilities for your Neovim.
STATUS: WIP
NVIM: v0.9.0-dev

PACKER
------
use {
  "dharmx/nvim-colo",
  event = "UIEnter",
  requires = "nvim-lua/plenary.nvim",
  config = function()
    require("colo").setup()
  end
}

